<br />Which means he's selling the ReproPak MMC1 at near marginal cost: compare the ReproPak (board only; 74HC161 sold separately) at $4 to the ReproPak MMC1 (with CPLD soldered on) at $9. Any reductions past that would probably have to come from cutting PCB manufacture/shipping cost.

		

